1. *Živi* srećno i zdravo! (Live happily and healthily!)
2. On *živi* u Beogradu. (He lives in Belgrade.)
3. *Žive* su stvari koje volim. (The things I love are alive.)
4. Ona *živi* sama. (She lives alone.)
5. On je *živeo* u Londonu. (He lived in London.)
6. Svi *živemo* u svetu punom nepravde. (We all live in a world full of injustice.)
7. Oni *žive* u luksuznom stanu. (They live in a luxurious apartment.)
8. Ona je *živela* u selu. (She used to live in a village.)
9. *Živite* svoj san. (Live your dream.)
10. Kako oni *žive* u takvim uslovima? (How do they live in such conditions?)